---
// BGP Leadership Section
// Pastor Mark Smith and Lady LaQuadia Smith
---

<section class="leadership-section py-20 px-[5%] bg-white" id="leadership">
  <div class="container max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-5" id="leadership-content">
    <!-- Section Heading -->
    <div class="section-heading text-center mb-[60px]">
      <h2 class="text-black text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
        Our Leadership
      </h2>
      <div class="heading-underline w-20 h-[3px] bg-[#9c8040] my-2.5 mx-auto"></div>
      <p class="section-tagline text-[#666] text-lg mt-4 italic">
        Lead with passion, vision, and authentic faith
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Pastor Mark -->
    <div class="leader-row flex flex-wrap items-center gap-10 mb-20">
      <div class="leader-image flex-1 min-w-[300px] text-center">
        <div class="image-container rounded-lg shadow-[0_4px_10px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] max-w-[450px] mx-auto overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src="/images/home/Pastor_Mark_HomePage-scaled.jpeg"
            alt="Pastor Mark Smith, Senior Pastor of Believers Gathering Place"
            class="w-full h-auto block"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="leader-content flex-1 min-w-[300px] px-5">
        <h3 class="text-black text-[28px] mb-2 font-bold">
          Pastor Mark Smith
        </h3>
        <p class="leader-title text-[#9c8040] text-lg font-semibold mb-5">
          Senior Pastor
        </p>
        <p class="leader-description mb-6 text-base leading-[1.7] text-[#444]">
          Discover the inspired direction of Pastor Mark Smith, Senior Leader of BGP, a man of great faith and vision who leads with steadfast devotion to God's mission.
        </p>
        <div class="leader-quote">
          <blockquote class="py-5 px-6 border-l-4 border-[#9c8040] italic my-8 text-[#333] bg-[rgba(156,128,64,0.08)] rounded-r-lg leading-relaxed">
            "We aim to see lives transformed by the grace of Christ. Join us in deeply living our faith, nurturing one another sincerely, and uplifting each other as a deeply unified family."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="leader-values flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-6">
          <span class="value-tag bg-[#fef7e0] text-[#9c8040] py-2 px-[18px] rounded-[20px] text-sm font-semibold border border-[rgba(156,128,64,0.2)]">
            Faith
          </span>
          <span class="value-tag bg-[#fef7e0] text-[#9c8040] py-2 px-[18px] rounded-[20px] text-sm font-semibold border border-[rgba(156,128,64,0.2)]">
            Service
          </span>
          <span class="value-tag bg-[#fef7e0] text-[#9c8040] py-2 px-[18px] rounded-[20px] text-sm font-semibold border border-[rgba(156,128,64,0.2)]">
            Unity
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Together -->
    <div class="leaders-together bg-[#f8f8f8] p-[50px] rounded-xl flex flex-wrap items-center gap-10 border border-[rgba(156,128,64,0.1)]">
      <div class="together-image flex-1 min-w-[300px] text-center">
        <div class="image-mask max-w-[500px] mx-auto overflow-hidden rounded-[50%_50%_0_50%] shadow-[0_8px_25px_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)]">
          <img
            src="/images/home/Mark_LadyQ_HomePage.jpeg"
            alt="Pastor Mark Smith and Lady LaQuadia Smith"
            class="w-full h-auto block"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="together-content flex-1 min-w-[300px] px-5">
        <h3 class="text-black mb-4 font-bold" style="font-size: clamp(20px, 3.5vw, 28px);">
          Pastor Mark and Lady&nbsp;LaQuadia
        </h3>
        <p class="mb-5 leading-[1.7] text-[#444]">
          Often called Lady Q, she embodies the essence of family at BGP, infusing the community with compassion and authenticity through her mentoring and relationship building.
        </p>
        <div class="leader-quote">
          <blockquote class="py-5 px-6 border-l-4 border-[#9c8040] italic my-8 text-[#333] bg-[rgba(156,128,64,0.08)] rounded-r-lg leading-relaxed">
            "At BGP, you become part of our family. No judgments are madeâ€”just love without conditions. Your value is recognized, and we pledge to support you on your journey."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-5 leading-[1.7] text-[#444]">
          Pastor Mark and Lady LaQuadia Smith are the heartfelt leaders of Believers Gathering Place, committed to fostering genuine faith, love, and unity within our church family.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-5 leading-[1.7] text-[#444]">
          Through their leadership, BGP has become a sanctuary of love and hope where people from all walks of life can find community, grow in their faith, and experience transformation.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-button">
          <a
            href="/"
            class="inline-block py-[15px] px-[35px] bg-[#9c8040] text-white no-underline rounded-md font-semibold text-base uppercase tracking-wide mt-[35px] hover:bg-[#b89654] transition-colors duration-300"
          >
            Plan Your Visit
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Mobile Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .leader-row,
    .leaders-together {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .leader-image,
    .leader-content,
    .together-image,
    .together-content {
      min-width: auto;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .leaders-together {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
